#compdef cacaserver
# Documentation: https://manpages.ubuntu.com/manpages/xenial/man1/cacaserver.1.html
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-17
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above.

# cacaserver's upstream manpage documents no command-line options. It reads
# libcaca animations on stdin and listens on TCP port 51914. Configuration is
# via environment (CACA_DRIVER, etc.).

_arguments -s -S \
  '*:caca animation file:_files'
